_sText:
Hey,

After much try&errors my map is finally done.
I like the look of the map, and with the lightning it is okay I think.
The layout could be a bit better, but it was okay when I played it with bots.

This map is good for big servers (20-40 players) so I recommend to play it with 20+ people or more.
Map contains:

HDR lightning.
40 spawnpoints.
Custom textures.

Maybe there will be an video soon :p
Hamster out
